Julie Ann Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Ann_Taylor 0 Julie Ann Taylor (born January 29, 1966) is an American voice actress who is best known for her role of Ai Tanabe in Planetes, Mutsumi Otohime in Love Hina, Yukari Hayasaka in Paradise Kiss and Taiga Fujimura in Fate/stay night among others. She is also credited as Julie Pickering, Jean Howard and Cricket Brown.
